#| "No, never. But the authors always welcome feedback. &marble; is licensed "
#| "under the <ulink url=\"http://www.gnu.org/licenses/licenses.html#LGPL"
#| "\">LGPL</ulink>, so you will never have to pay for this program."
msgid ""
"No, never. But the authors always welcome feedback. &marble; is licensed "
"under the <ulink url=\"https://www.gnu.org/licenses/licenses.html#LGPL"
"\">LGPL</ulink>, so you will never have to pay for this program."
msgstr ""
"Non, nunca. Aínda que os autores sempre agradecerán as súas opinións. "
"&marble; publícase baixo a <ulink url=\"http://www.gnu.org/licenses/licenses."
"html#LGPL\">LGPL</ulink>, polo que nunca terá que pagar por este programa."

